{"tid":2337693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"惟有飲者L其M（LM狗）班弱智fans快入黎睇下隻死發情狗公啦","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T06:47:53.000Z","uid":343520,"like":35,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2f64540b8c0c18651f377c93ddece92560d2058f","tid":2337693,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"唔知咩事嘅人可以先去睇下呢個po。<br />\n<br />\n惟有飲者L其M 同佢班弱智fans入一入黎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2337372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2337372</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">簡單嚟講，LM狗行為狗公，發情隨便騷擾女性，證據確鑿</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F95MHwS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF95MHwS.png&h=42e4efd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日佢終於<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>縮係人地個post度回應我嘅指控</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oMsrVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oMsrVN.png&h=ac99c873&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rs1oKHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRs1oKHs.png&h=84177012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>比我屌柒完就開始扮假膠？你形容得咁詳細又有曬時間地點又重酬，真定假邊個知呀？<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n惟有飲者L其M（LM狗），你敢開post尋人唔敢開post道歉，你係咪咁撚廢，之前就由得班傻閪fans衝出黎做擋箭牌，你阿媽教你逃避責任架？定你有爺生無乸教架？"},{"pid":"f8fedc0f6e88b6d91c0fcf45eaab428bb360dd72","tid":2337693,"uid":31765,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"本身都覺得你係假膠<br />\n但呢次真心撐你<br />\n對事不對人<br />\n條仆街真係狗公嚟"},{"pid":"50d1db9a95abd93ff48fa9b415de30d0c64ea17e","tid":2337693,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"痴線 放過人啦 <br />\n咪再推好無<br />\n係咪要搞到人地自殺先安樂！！？"},{"pid":"c25b607a9a009c143c6316f1ba72e8